Interface MarkRelatedValues


  • public interface MarkRelatedValues
    Represents some values related to a mark.

    • Method Summary

    • Method Detail

      • getOwner

        org.bukkit.entity.Player getOwner()
        Returns the owner of the mark. With this value, different players could have different marks with a same key. It could be null and the provider should just return the static marks which don't have an owner. When it is specified, the provider should still returns the marks owned by the owner and also the static marks.
        Returns:
        The owner.

      • getPermissible

        org.bukkit.permissions.Permissible getPermissible()
        Returns permissible trying to get the mark. The provider should only return the marks the permissible have access to. Sometimes the provider can cast it to Player to get other information and decide whether the player having access to a mark. It could be null and the provider should just return all the marks.
        Returns:
        The permissible.
